PROCESS
 
Sell Discipline:
 


35% price decline relative to benchmark (without near-term visible recovery).

 

Unanticipated key management change.

 

Achieve price targets.

 

15% maximum weighting for any single stock for Select Value, 12% for Core Value and Small Cap Value. MVM Opportunity is an Absolute Return product and can hold up to 100% cash.





 
 












