Company Overview of McClain Value Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
McClain Value Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to individuals, high net worth individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, pooled investment vehicles, charitable organizations, corporations, state or municipal government entities, trusts, foundations, and endowments. It manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. The firm invests in the equity markets of the United States. It typically invests in the value stocks of small cap and all cap companies. The firm employs a fundamental analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach to create its equity portfolios. It benchmarks the performance of its equity portfolios against the S&P...
McClain Value Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to individuals, high net worth individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, pooled investment vehicles, charitable organizations, corporations, state or municipal government entities, trusts, foundations, and endowments. It manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. The firm invests in the equity markets of the United States. It typically invests in the value stocks of small cap and all cap companies. The firm employs a fundamental analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach to create its equity portfolios. It benchmarks the performance of its equity portfolios against the S&P 500 Index, Russell 2000 Index, and Russell 2000 Value Index. The firm conducts in-house research to make its investments. McClain Value Management, LLC was founded in 2001 and is based in New Canaan, Connecticut.
